arts.ttl: Frankfurt and Augsburg share spoils in thrilling 2-2 draw at Deutsche Bank Park
arts.sum: Eintracht Frankfurt and FC Augsburg played out a thrilling 2-2 draw on Bundesliga Matchday 13, with all four goals coming in a dramatic second half. Hugo Ekitiké and Can Uzun struck for Frankfurt, while Phillip Tietz and Samuel Essende found the net for Augsburg.

arts.ttl: 15:30 Kickoffs: Musiala leads FCB "reaction", Frankfurt draw, Bayer extend winning streak
arts.sum: German record champions FC Bayern München have opened up a six-point-gap at the top of the Bundesliga table after they won their Saturday 15:30 kickoff while second-place Eintracht Frankfurt drew theirs. Elsewhere, defending champs Leverkusen made it five straight wins on-the-bounce while bottom dwellers Bochum and Kiel both lost.

arts.ttl: Frankfurt vs. Augsburg preview: Eintracht hope to recover from Pokal mishap
arts.sum: Former FC Augsburg player Dino Toppmöller prepares will hope to get his German Eagles back on track when the FCA pay a visit to Deutsche Bank Park on Saturday afternoon.

arts.ttl: Toppmöller declares Theate fit for Augsburg, commits to Marmoush and Ekitiké
arts.sum: Eintracht Frankfurt trainer Dino Toppmöller discussed the state of his squad following Wednesday's shock Pokal defeat at his Friday pre-match presser.

arts.ttl: Weekend acca predictions: Five teams to back across Europe
arts.sum: No shortage of quality domestic action taking place across Europe this weekend and Aaron Rogan is on hand with a five-team acca for consideration.

arts.ttl: Eintracht Frankfurt interested in bringing Paul Wanner in on loan

arts.ttl: Kevin Trapp named November Player of the Month
arts.sum: The Eintracht community has voted the team captain as the Mainova Player of the Month, winning a tight race against Hugo Ekitiké and Mario Götze.

arts.ttl: Preview: Eintracht Frankfurt vs. Augsburg - prediction, team news, lineups
arts.sum: Sports Mole previews Saturday's Bundesliga clash between Eintracht Frankfurt and Augsburg, including predictions, team news and possible lineups.
